{"tid":529101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈唔好比五毛長輩湊你個仔！","createTime":"2018-01-14T13:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T14:59:15.000Z","uid":148011,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"90d3e732767c42963e52dc8fb97751bf43853b7c","tid":529101,"uid":148011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:55:00.000Z","msg":"有時聽人問，依家仲有幾多後生仔會係五毛？<br />\n其實係超多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做開私補，十個有九個小學雞都係五毛黎，講野口吻同廢老一樣，會講「啲人示威，比着以前喺大陸車死晒佢地」「香港點可以獨立，我地啲水都係大陸比」「啲人示威就抵比警察打」<br />\n<br />\n真係無誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一問之下原來全部都係老豆老母要返工，比老人家湊。班老野好似訓練紅衛兵咁，日哦夜哦開時事論壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n親眼見過啲老友記抱住BB唱國歌洗腦。依家班小學雞好鍾意唱國歌痴撚線，連國歌法都熟晒，好有sense，可惜係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有生仔睇實啲，唔係第時大個激死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ababed38331e48946bae8a955bf0a1fbb2266d1","tid":529101,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:05:01.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01944726c1c2a6788d93b82b6e986623b2562ec6","tid":529101,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d01950960aa47e60493241a64239afd91d30547e","tid":529101,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:52:57.000Z","msg":"我趵親中嘅親戚，我不嬲當佢哋五毛咁當眾開佢哋拖"},{"pid":"d6e9fd62a854bf403241aa677a193f1af0bf2d7c","tid":529101,"uid":155747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:54:23.000Z","msg":"身邊有生仔嘅，藍絲多過黃絲本土"},{"pid":"2d6f2d00c8ec2c7b147f6c0efcf3fd6d5311416b","tid":529101,"uid":148011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01944726c1c2a6788d93b82b6e986623b2562ec6","tid":529101,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:55:22.000Z","msg":"五毛有老豆老母既咩？"},{"pid":"510c15c547f6068e51362cc9e29911f0d73a29a8","tid":529101,"uid":155747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6e9fd62a854bf403241aa677a193f1af0bf2d7c","tid":529101,"uid":155747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:54:23.000Z","msg":"身邊有生仔嘅，藍絲多過黃絲本土"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:57:55.000Z","msg":"可能同性格有關, 黃絲本土多崇尚自由主義, 藍絲就傳統啲"},{"pid":"e3a03a8d3517b7ec54119554b1c34c744e2b05dc","tid":529101,"uid":155747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"510c15c547f6068e51362cc9e29911f0d73a29a8","tid":529101,"uid":155747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6e9fd62a854bf403241aa677a193f1af0bf2d7c","tid":529101,"uid":155747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:54:23.000Z","msg":"身邊有生仔嘅，藍絲多過黃絲本土"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:57:55.000Z","msg":"可能同性格有關, 黃絲本土多崇尚自由主義, 藍絲就傳統啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"同埋身邊啲藍絲有錢啲"}]}